| exportedClass item |
Display clear.
Transcript show: 'PACKAGE SOURCE'.
Transcript cr.
Workspace fileOutPackageNamed: 'Tools'.
Transcript show: Workspace contents.
Transcript cr.
exportedClass := KernelInstaller classNamed: 'PackageEcho'.
item := exportedClass new.
item setValue: 'ROUNDTRIP'.
Transcript show: item value.
Transcript cr.
exportedClass cr.
Transcript show: 'TOOLS'.
